race.description: Wdc Country Stampede Qualifier Open Hcp
race.comment: DEHORNED UNICORN (2) returned in good order with a close-up second at Gaynah and will have come on with that run now under the belt. Rates the testing material against this line-up. SMILING ZAC (4) has a handy record over this sprint trip with four wins and five placings from 14 attempts. Looms as the main danger. TIJUANA TWO STEP (5) has put back-to-back wins together and is racing with a lot of confidence of late. Genuine top-three prospects on recent efforts. The well-related MEDALS (8) (half to 2xG3 winner and G2 placed Raiment) doesn't know how to run a bad race and is a must for the multiples.
